CustomField.description: This field shows either the Total Prospective formula field used on Single Institution records OR the Total Prospective roll up summary used on Multi Institution records
CustomField.formula: IF( Total_Prospective_RollUp__c != 0 || Total_Prospective_RollUp__c != null, Total_Prospective_RollUp__c, Total_Prospective__c )
CustomField.label: Total # Prospective
